:

*1. "Ona je glavna zvezda šoua" (She is the main star of the show). 
2. "On je dobio priliku da nastupi u šouu" (He got a chance to perform in the show). 
3. "Ovo je pravi šou-biznis" (This is the real show business). 
4. "Šou je bio pun događaja" (The show was full of events). 
5. "Ona je bila voditelj šoua" (She was the host of the show). 
6. "On je završio šou sa izuzetnim nastupom" (He finished the show with an outstanding performance).